title: Electric Circuits (8th Edition): Nilsson [Solution Manual]
description:
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Electric-Circuits-8th-James-Nilsson/dp/0131989251" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.amazon.com/Electric-Circuits-8th-James-Nilsson/dp/0131989251</a> 

This is the book from which the solutions manual is from...and yes, it is the 8th edition. 

This should be the latest out there and anyone who is in this class probably needs this. The painstaking algebra on some chapters simply forced me in uploading the solutions manual. Algebra should be done using maple or some other computing program...but I digress. 

This does have all of the chapters (1-18) including 2-port systems..which I noticed some torrents do not have.

Information should be free, so please, keep uploading E-books! 

This is me giving back to a great community.
